{
  "stem": "22883.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's one document that's missing, and he doesn't remember whom he gave it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he asked me if I got such a document.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, no, I don't-- I don't ask any document.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he knew that one document was missing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this document we kept with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when we-- there was opportunity to do something, to get out of Dubno.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Apparently, I got the message that the management from Warsaw is coming for inspection-- how we are doing here, how we are working for the Germans, and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were paid for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I heard Saturday from this Polish company.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so definitely, there was the case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came for the weekend from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, they came to-- to see us, me and-- and Lilian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were talking, and we gave them impression that Lilian is pregnant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she has-- because of course, we don't want to have a child-- she has to go to Warsaw to make abortion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Apparently, this trick worked, and they believed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I asked them to take Lilian with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, because they have the papers, so they-- they could take Lilian and go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the next day, I-- we decided that I will go using this stolen [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] traveling document, that I will do by my-- myself, alone, next day also to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we will meet in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Interesting at that time that those people, the Polish people, they were suspecting something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all the day-- when Lilian left, the day before it was Saturday, she left with those people from Warsaw, management people.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
